data.description: This 3BDR/2BA/2CAR golf course frontage home in the Meadowlands community is For Sale. Located in Calabash, NC, this one owner home presents an array of desirable features, promising a lifestyle of comfort and picturesque views. With an open floor plan and high ceilings, there is ample room for family and guests.  Enjoy special occasions in the formal dining room. The owner's suite offers a spacious walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom complete with a walk-in tub and double vanity. A separate den/office provides flexibility for your unique needs. Right off the three-season porch, is an expansive kitchen featuring a breakfast bar, center island, solid surface counter, crown molding, pantry and plenty of cabinets. There is a laundry room right off the Great Room. The two car garage has a door screen which is an easy way to make the garage into extra living space. Step outside to your private backyard, where you can enjoy the natural beauty of the surroundings. The Meadowlands Golf Community offers an array of amenities, including a clubhouse, a community outdoor pool, and a fitness center, ensuring you can stay active and engaged within the community.  Combining indoor and outdoor living, this home allows you to enjoy the best of coastal living and the pleasures of the golf course fairway. Don't miss out on this opportunity to live in a beautiful home surrounded by nature and the finest community amenities. Home will be sold furnished, with few exceptions. Call today to schedule a viewing and make this your next home-sweet-home.
